{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["The Lucky Crane\n\n<size=45>Chapter 4 - Zuikaku & Master Mikasa<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Evening - Practice Area","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","bgm":"battle-1"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Splendid! Now come at me and attack!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Okay!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Zuikaku's planes released their dummy bombs over Mikasa, achieving a marvelous direct hit.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/plane"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ouch!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"x":15,"dur":0.1,"number":3}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Sweet, sweet victory! ... Hey, Master Mikasa, what happened? Are you okay?!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I-I am fine... I must say, that was a spectacular attack! You have made phenomenal progress since your training began!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Thank you, Master Mikasa! ... Hey, Commander, am I awesome, or what?!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","dur":0.15,"number":3,"y":30}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Ahahahah! Okay, I'm awesome, but maybe not THAT awesome~! All right, now I should be one step closer to surpassing the Grey Ghost!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Then, next time, I'll be able to protect my sister and my friends...!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Commander, could you put the Grey Ghost and me together for the next sortie? I'll nab that MVP, I swear it!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Zuikaku grinned as she turned around and headed back towards the base.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1"},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Commander, do you have a moment?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Zuikaku may not seem like it, but within her lies the strong desire to thoroughly prove her worth. In other words: she will one day drive herself into a corner.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Her desires go beyond merely wanting to surpass the Grey Ghost. She wants to shoulder the burdens of Shoukaku, her Sakura Empire brethren, the entire world, and even you, Commander.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Commander, I must ask a favor of you... A favor as Zuikaku's mentor, a favor as an individual...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If the burdens she carries grow too heavy... then I want you to be by her side and support her.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"......","withoutPainting":true,"actor":0,"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Ahah, that's what I wanted to hear. You have my gratitude.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305110,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"RUIHE4","fadeOut":1.5}